### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">هُوَ ٱلَّذِى يُحْىِۦ وَيُمِيتُ ۖ فَإِذَا قَضَىٰٓ أَمْرًا فَإِنَّمَا يَقُولُ لَهُۥ كُن فَيَكُونُ</span>

### English

He is the One Who gives life and causes death. When He decrees a matter, He simply tells it, “Be!” And it is!